puts "   1. Open UbiCloud dashboard: http://localhost:3000"
puts "   2. Navigate to Virtual Machines"
puts "   3. Click 'Create VM' and select 'On-Premises Data Center'"
puts "   4. Create your first VM!"
puts ""
